19
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:08,320
What do you mean three times?

20
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:09,320
One turn is enough.

21
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:10,120
One turn.

22
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:12,840
Try it.

23
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:22,520
Cars nowadays

24
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:24,180
are different from your time.

25
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:26,120
They're all smart cars now.

26
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:33,280
If only we were

27
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:35,360
that lucky back then.

28
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,160
Yaozu,

29
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:43,760
this time,

30
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:48,560
I'm afraid I can't make it to the end with you.

31
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:51,040
Hanwen, stop talking nonsense.

32
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:52,120
Hang in there.

33
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:58,720
I don't think I can hold on this time.

34
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,360
Those bastards

35
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:10,180
