39
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:19,920
Hanwen.

40
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:22,440
We've made it through so many times.

41
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,720
We will this time too.

42
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,960
Once we get past this bamboo forest,

43
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,220
I'll find you a doctor.

44
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:38,280
Yaozu.

45
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,000
Promise me

46
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,800
you'll help me

47
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,800
keep this safe.

48
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:45,760
What is this?

49
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:48,040
I'm afraid I can't

50
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:49,040
bring it

51
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:52,120
to Xiao Pushao.

52
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,880
I didn't let Ah Ma down.

53
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:07,240
Hanwen.

54
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:13,840
Right.

55
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,890
You have to hold on until

56
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,740
