63
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:37,170
Nanyang is waiting for you.

64
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:39,370
Ah Ma is waiting for you too.

65
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:43,240
Right.

66
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:44,850
And Xiao Pushao.

67
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:46,240
Yes.

68
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,200
Do you think

69
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:01,240
Xiao Pushao

70
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:07,640
will go back to Nanyang with me?

71
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:11,720
You promised to build her a bamboo house.

72
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,250
You must keep your promise.

73
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:16,560
Then you'll have a home here

74
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,200
and a home in Nanyang.

75
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,400
Hanwen.

76
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:36,840
Hanwen.

77
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:38,960
Hanwen.

78
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,720
Hanwen.

79
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:43,120
Wake up.

80
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:45,240
Hanwen.

81
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:04,520
Lianzi.

82
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:07,320
This lotus seed is also called Lianxin.

83
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:10,040
It's like our hearts are connected.

84
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:13,360
Yes, wearing it is like being with Grandma.

85
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:19,130
Hanwen will definitely come back safely.

86
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:23,320
When Grandma sees me come back,

87
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:26,040
