141
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:46,020
From then on, there are no more Nanyang overseas Chinese mechanics in the world.

142
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:50,320
But the deeds and patriotic spirit of the Nanyang overseas Chinese mechanics

143
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:52,720
have always inspired and guided us.

144
00:10:55,640 --> 00:10:56,080
No.

145
00:10:56,920 --> 00:10:59,440
Maybe the mechanic is right beside us.

146
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:00,960
Or maybe

147
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:04,080
