148
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:10,360
The stories of the overseas Chinese's patriotism will be known by more people.

149
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:12,090
I believe they certainly will.

150
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:30,290
Now that our country is in trouble,

151
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:37,100
I, Qiantang, am determined to send my grandson Lin Yaozu back to the country to fight in the war of resistance.

152
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:42,080
Grandpa.

153
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:46,020
The motherland you care about

154
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:49,360
