158
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:07,080
These family letters

159
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:09,140
carry extraordinary significance.

160
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:11,540
They also record that period of history.

161
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:13,600
Look.

162
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:15,660
They have been protected by the state

163
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:17,320
and have a special name,

164
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:18,240
Qiaopi.

165
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:20,200
Qiaopi.

166
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:26,360
Every Qiaopi contains a different story of overseas Chinese.

167
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:46,640
Do you three know when

168
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:49,960
the Japanese army launched the full-scale invasion of China?

169
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:51,840
July 7, 1937,

170
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,120
