177
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:12,640
drove the Japanese invaders out of our Chinese territory.

178
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,120
Wanding, Yunnan.

179
00:13:14,160 --> 00:13:14,600
Right,

180
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:15,760
Wanding Bridge.

181
00:13:26,800 --> 00:13:28,530
I didn't come back for nothing.

182
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:32,840
Perhaps this is destiny.

183
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:37,220
Let's continue our tour this way.

184
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:47,600
That is...

185
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,520
Mr. Jiageng.
